Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友情  恋爱  推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那样的约定的话就可以坚持到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.48,0:00:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不合季节的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的心情揭穿案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看穿真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.48,0:00:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩  头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伴儿  你要振作一点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.43,0:01:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保持住清醒的意识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人  您要冷静呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.73,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等片刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不是撞痕又不是擦伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了  干扰急救可不行呀  小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入意识不清的病危状态了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下医院的抢救工作也会相当艰难呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  简直是丝毫不曾察觉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝高之后  酩酊大醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.33,0:02:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生可是边睡边断案的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛  毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非人称“沉睡的小五郎”的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位毛利先生么  那位侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是“名侦探”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  这可真是失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经获得了上级的批准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦劳您一定要协助我们的调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.13,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上级的  这个不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.73,0:03:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱与幽灵与地球遗产（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.03,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要被列为地球遗产了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然发生这样的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我也是这个村子里长大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望您能争分夺秒尽快破案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.23,0:03:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  既然您这么恳切地请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小五郎一定全力相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那您就尽管放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.23,0:03:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么恕我直言毛利先生  谁是凶手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会真是什么幽灵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道些什么呢  你们这些小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  果然还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  就是那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  柯南你不是也看见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  只不过是什么东西看起来像她罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道又是洗过的衣服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  多亏步美看花了眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才能察觉凶犯逃走的方向呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个方向的话  死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像无法通行到村外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶犯还没有逃离这个村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.03,0:04:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在不像专程从村外闯进来行凶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连同游客一并算上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.53,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在凶犯就混在这个鬼泽乡的众人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  你们到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必理会他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们所说的那些  连外行都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.73,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  你们可不要干扰查案呀  各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有件更应该引起我们注意的重要事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在白天观光时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里系好了绳索并藏了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后  深夜从村外潜入时用到了那根绳索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人应该是除去毛利先生您所住的永仓家以外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且就在住宿本村的游客之内  是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是毛利先生  佩服  佩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.03,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真是太抬举我了  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂且不管这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.93,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是  犯人在那里干了什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那阁楼顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元太  你不要推我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.13,0:06:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点  我们还要再上一层呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是个小偷而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  究竟打算从这里偷些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来  还是我看错了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然柯南都那么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得好像是看花眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是想偷什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是绝对是在找什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在这的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生被刺伤的现场可真是一目了然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在对面那间屋子也会看得一清二楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南  发现什么了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿  有什么情况么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰  会中毒发炎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是漆树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  永仓先生的手确实是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说永仓先生昨天经过了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是昨天那个令人讨厌的家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  是他将永仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么村民们会围着他吵嚷起来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我倒是知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这儿之前  我在杂志上读到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说  本来这个村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,围绕着是否要申请地球遗产的问题而发生了分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不希望再增加游客的反对派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和希望这村子能名闻天下的推进派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.43,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生应该是那个推进派的代表呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候永仓先生说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是被谁指使的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.03,0:08:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那帮家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“那帮家伙”原来指的是反对派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给警察来处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快些回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能  我们要在这里讨个说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那家伙逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调查员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.33,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地球遗产登记委员会派遣来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有像这样隐藏自己的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.23,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公平地判断是否有申请地球遗产的价值的专职调查员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.23,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个人的话  这只是表面上的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从各地上缴的自治费用中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为评估人员的活动经费收取可观的贿赂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧  川治先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在说些什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要装傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在被害者附近出现过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经掌握了证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来也向永仓先生勒索贿赂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.13,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却不料碰了个钉子  所以你才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要乱开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是向他提过钱的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也确实被拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只好就此作罢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备今天就回去  昨晚便早早入睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一步都没出去过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老奸巨滑的你哪能这么轻易就放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会相信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此我才确实放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据我多年来的经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.13,0:09:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样死缠烂打下去也不会有活动经费进腰包的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生的巡视记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据当天的记录来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在巡查过第九幢房子时还盖着“无异常情况”的章印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生遇袭被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在已经盖上章正走向第九幢房子的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.83,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你住宿的石岗先生家旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说又不是我决定要住在那家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么有谁看到你入睡了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为当时只有我自己  所以没有任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是我干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺伤别人这种愚蠢行为我是不可能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果  川治先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.73,0:10:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被警方作为恐吓及杀人未遂案件的重要嫌疑人带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而关于其杀人未遂的嫌疑却完全缺乏证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于潜入永仓家的情况也完全不详
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.53,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来案件似乎是解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.33,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福终于逮捕了川治这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿我们是不是要庆祝一下喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很想说“好呀～”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为有被老婆审讯的危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.43,0:11:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是祸不单行呀  永仓先生家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草草解决了案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  这样反而不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祸不单行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔说的是他们家的儿子永仓荣治吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很大的意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信荣治是无辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美找他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起荣治他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的家伙已经不是我的儿子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那件事也算上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.23,0:11:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十天前村里刚举行过神器转移的祭祀活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.03,0:11:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行了久违三十年的茅屋房顶的修整重葺工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.83,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且把各家各户的屋子移动到了现在的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移动了  那样巨大的房屋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.13,0:12:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  那些地基如此的新原来是因为这个缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过令人震惊的还远不止这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.53,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半个月以前永仓家所在的位置是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.73,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对　好象是从这里搬到了现在的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.53,0:12:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和原本在那里的乙泽家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好调换了位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是神器转移什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.93,0:12:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那儿不是整个村里看起来最好的地点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说是永仓家作为申请地球遗产的推进派代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强行搬迁到那儿去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不少人那么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真像呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你们是说这间屋子和永仓家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是夜里的话认错了也不是没可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.33,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许犯人的动机与是否申请地球遗产全无关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说只是单纯地把两栋房子给弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  忽然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别  别跑这么快嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面也一模一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.53,0:13:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在永仓先生家里时应该是在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  太精美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  新一呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.33,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那桩宝石抢劫案时被盗的宝石呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来怎么样是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像还没有找到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.23,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方得出的结论是早就被犯罪份子处理掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是还没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪犯逃亡时把那间宝石店的鉴定师绑架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推测说大概是人质没用之后就被杀害了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　好烫呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才　没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点小事而已  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧么  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是交给警察比较
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  你的声音太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是这真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快  毛利先生  请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然  真凶是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜恐怕会在那里出现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然还是来了  大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等了你很久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次绝不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.43,0:15:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着  出来散散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果迷了路  和永仓家还真像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些宝石是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.13,0:15:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是你一个月前在邻村的宝石店里抢来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.93,0:15:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在说什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装傻也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.63,0:15:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔　你就是杀害了永仓荣治并且将其伪装成自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝石抢劫案的主犯  对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣治哥哥好像负债累累吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是你便以此为由强行要挟他作帮凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  抢劫宝石和杀害警卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实都是大叔你一个人干的  对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.43,0:16:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道你在说些什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.73,0:16:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡过程中经荣治带路来到了这鬼泽村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.73,0:16:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把抢来的宝石藏在了已经废弃的乙泽家的空屋内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你没有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半个月后村里会调换房屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.03,0:16:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后　你便把罪行都嫁祸给了荣治哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀害了他  并使现场看似自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.73,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而后  又装成观光游客再次来到这个村子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想取走藏起来的赃物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在左手里拿着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是那些宝石么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.03,0:16:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚趁永仓先生外出巡夜不在之机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.83,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你寻找宝石时被我们发现便从窗口逃逸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说根本不是从外部潜入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而本来就在那栋房子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.53,0:17:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这一切却被在外巡夜的永仓先生撞见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在永仓先生匆匆忙忙返回自家的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡查记录上印章的顺序之所以可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  我不过是个糟老头子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是来旅行的罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些宝石也不过是偶然发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.43,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既不是上了年纪的人也不是游客 我们很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为早就注意到了你右眼眶周围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是放大镜的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被当作人质劫持又被认为已经惨遭杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去向不明的鉴定师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你  坂木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.13,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过自从犯人自杀以后 我就一直很害怕躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.63,0:18:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在才终于鼓起勇气来取走宝石的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.33,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话你们打算怎么办呢  小鬼们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.43,0:18:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说  你承认昨夜曾在永仓家三层寻找宝石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又能怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之后你从窗口逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺伤永仓先生的罪行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀是呀  我喝得太多醉得昏天黑地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说根本不可能进行那样的犯罪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.03,0:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你什么时候在哪里碰到漆树了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起喝酒的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.83,0:18:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和永仓先生可都还没有中毒发炎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.03,0:18:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问问一起就餐的人就能马上查实了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那可正是你们俩曾在同一时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同一地点的绝佳证据呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全村栽种漆树的地方可是独一无二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下结案了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的小鬼们  到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户川柯南  侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们　少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑  还不快给我闪开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能被你几个小鬼抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 　把荣治还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把荣治还给我呀　还给我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  就是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮  步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是逼真演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯卡影后级的学院水准呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不过安静地站在这里而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站着  那刚才的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雾  是雾  好好看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是岚烟呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.83,0:20:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飞机上或山顶经常能看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么  如此说来  那些也都是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.93,0:20:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  世界上有什么不能用科学与推理来解释呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢您昨天的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.03,0:22:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.93,0:22:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福  成功阻止了犯人逃亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是您呀  毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.33,0:22:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我松代  真是心服口服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心  心服口服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.23,0:22:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是呀  是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想再见你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.83,0:23:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕你是幽灵也好  真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.93,0:23:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美　快点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.63,0:23:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了  等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.23,0:23:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调换位置的两栋茅草屋  各归原位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.23,0:23:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说后来伤愈的永仓先生感悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.03,0:23:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是在儿子幼年青梅竹马的朋友真美的灵魂指引下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.33,0:23:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儿子死因的真相才得以重见天日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然作为侦探  坚持理论和推理的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.83,0:23:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不会相信这些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.43,0:23:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后  经过了两个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.93,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼泽乡作为地球遗产正式被登记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.85,0:23:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟犯罪这样的社会阴暗做斗争就是我侦探的本职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这大叔做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.87,0:23:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.69,0:24:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没把天线收回去真是个粗心的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.39,0:24:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是 他想让人听到铃声并发现手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.99,0:24:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以故意藏到那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.64,0:24:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.91,0:24:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三千日圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.77,0:24:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.86,0:24:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.27,0:24:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被遗忘的手机(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.63,0:24:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.56,0:24:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电话号码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.30,0:24:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.22,0:24:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利侦探事务所一楼的咖啡厅叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.85,0:24:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就是买啤酒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.32,0:00:25.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,近日时常梦见你突然离我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.21,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,面对惶惑不安的我 你依然无声无息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一双温暖的手紧握在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.06,0:00:42.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠的五指仿佛缤纷的花朵竞色争奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.09,0:00:49.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使停驻于忧郁隐晦的霏霏霪雨 你的身影依然那么粲然夺目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.23,0:00:55.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向着你我约定过的温柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.90,0:01:01.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,而今两个人依然齐肩攀越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,遥望你为我彩绘的梦幻季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:14.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,暂别的时日可以令爱更强烈 直至岁月翻过那一页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向着你我约定过的温柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.89,0:01:25.86,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,无谓的逃避只会迷途无措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.39,0:01:31.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,纵然漫无标识的路千曲百折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.96,0:01:39.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1450)}依循彼此的信任与爱相携 直至步入那温柔世界…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.39,0:21:13.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的视线相遇之前 心就已经决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.25,0:21:23.91,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如同正午的月亮一般 虽然看不见 但是知道它在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.79,0:21:36.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是孤独 就算是幸福 一个人的时候又怎能分辨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.94,0:21:47.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的相遇 如同在深海中游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.68,0:22:01.03,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沐浴在光芒下呼吸 寻找我们两人的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.26,0:22:12.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在围绕着升起又落下的太阳 旋转的这个星球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.90,0:22:19.63,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧缓缓起伏的海面上的月亮
